2 December 2008The directors-general of the Economic, Investment and Employment Cluster of Government will brief members of the media on the progress made in the implementation of cluster programmes.The briefing will be chaired by Director-General Tshediso Matona, of the Department of Trade and Industry.Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: Wednesday, 3 December 2008 Time: 10:30 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNote: There will be a link-up to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape TownEnquiries Harold Maloka (Pretoria) Cell: 082 847 9799Colin Cruywagen (Cape Town) Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)